-- TABLE-UK mortgage approvals hit 12-month low in Aug - BBA
-- 
-- Tue Sep 23, 2014 04:54AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Sept 23 (Reuters) - Mortgage approvals for house purchases fell to their lowest level in 12 months in August, but were still 5.2 percent up on the previous year, seasonally adjusted data from the British Bankers' Assocation showed on Tuesday.

